
Ranger Help for: encircle
=========================

SYNTAX:      encircle <target>
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             underground,mountain,arctic,barren,outside
SLOT COST:   4
BASE SP:     30 sp
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to use his or her superior knowledge of the
outdoors to gain an advantage against an opponent by circling around
it. While circling, if you use an attack type skill when BEHIND an
opponent, you do additional damage, since the opponent can't defend
itself from behind. But, some other skills such as firing your ranger's
bow won't work, since your moving around and never have the time to
stop and aim your bow.

